<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>After a recent update to Zend_Loader, Zend_Filter_Input began emitting warning errors for non-existent classes. This is because Zend_Filter_Input was using a base 'namespace' property to derive the base name for both filters and validators and would try both before matching the correct class name.</p>

<p>This needs to be refactored to allow Zend_Loader_PluginLoader to locate the correct class name more efficiently and to also refine the API for Zend_Filter_Input to allow better distinction between filter and validator namespaces.</p>

    </div>
</div>

